We believe in connecting with each other not in spite of our differences, but because of our differences. 

To celebrate difference this season, we’ve teamed up with Hong Kong artist @zlism to bring our 2021 Pride collection to life. Through a series of playful illustrations and designs, the collection underlines our belief that everybody is welcome, no matter how you identify.

Link in bio for more on our initiatives in commemoration of Pride 2021.
